title: LF D3+ toplaner for OOL. top 8 team
body:
Team Unkown, is currently looking for a main roster top laner, for the last week of OOL, currently in the top 8 for points and looking towards top 2 for a spot to fight for OCS. Requirements for acceptance is D3+ for more info on the team add me in game.

IGN: Minigorophin, Bronze fabbbyyy
